      "next": "4",
      "meta": {
        "file": "examples\\recursive_minimal_decomposition.rail",
        "line": 37
      }
    },
    "4": {
      "type": "Ask",
      "instruction": "请说明这次拆解的分析目的，例如用于制定行动方案、设计指标、分配责任、定位失败原因，还是做概念理解。",
      "next": "5",
      "meta": {
        "file": "examples\\recursive_minimal_decomposition.rail",
        "line": 41
      }
    },
    "5": {
